# WeatherCast – Feature Expansion Plan

Implementing **15 practical new features** grouped into 6 phases. All data remains mock (no API key needed). Real API integration is optional and can be layered in later by swapping [WeatherService](file:///c:/Users/AkshayakumarKM/.gemini/antigravity/playground/Angular/src/app/services/weather.service.ts#199-223).

> [!NOTE]
> Weather sounds and side-by-side compare are deferred — sounds need audio assets, and compare adds significant UI complexity beyond scope. All other 15 features below will be fully implemented.

---

## Phase 1 – Foundation Services

### [MODIFY] [weather.model.ts](file:///c:/Users/AkshayakumarKM/.gemini/antigravity/playground/Angular/src/app/models/weather.model.ts)
Add new interfaces:
- `HourlyForecast` – hour label, temp, conditionCode, rainProb
- `AirQuality` – aqi (0-500), pm25, co2, ozone, label ('Good'|'Moderate'|'Unhealthy'…)
- `WeatherAlert` – title, message, severity ('info'|'warning'|'danger')
- `HistoricalDay` – date, high, low
- Extend [WeatherData](file:///c:/Users/AkshayakumarKM/.gemini/antigravity/playground/Angular/src/app/models/weather.model.ts#34-38) to include `hourly`, `airQuality`, `alerts[]`, `historical[]`

### [NEW] `src/app/services/settings.service.ts`
- `unit$: BehaviorSubject<'C'|'F'>` — temperature unit, persisted in `localStorage`
- `theme$: BehaviorSubject<'dark'|'light'>` — theme, persisted in `localStorage`
- `toggleUnit()`, `toggleTheme()` methods
- On init, reads saved values from `localStorage` and applies `data-theme` attr on `<body>`

### [NEW] `src/app/services/favourites.service.ts`
- `favourites$: BehaviorSubject<string[]>` — list of favourite city names
- `toggle(city)`, `isFavourite(city)`, persisted in `localStorage`

### [NEW] `src/app/services/history.service.ts`
- `history$: BehaviorSubject<string[]>` — last 5 searched cities
- `add(city)`, `clear()`, persisted in `localStorage`

---

## Phase 2 – Navbar Upgrades

### [MODIFY] [navbar.ts](file:///c:/Users/AkshayakumarKM/.gemini/antigravity/playground/Angular/src/app/navbar/navbar.ts) / [navbar.html](file:///c:/Users/AkshayakumarKM/.gemini/antigravity/playground/Angular/src/app/navbar/navbar.html) / [navbar.css](file:///c:/Users/AkshayakumarKM/.gemini/antigravity/playground/Angular/src/app/navbar/navbar.css)
- Inject `SettingsService`, `FavouritesService`, `HistoryService`
- Add **°C/°F toggle** pill button
- Add **🌙/☀️ theme toggle** icon button  
- Show **recent history chips** (click to re-search) in collapsible strip below search
- Show **⭐ favourite cities** quick chips below history
- Add **📍 Geolocation** button — calls `navigator.geolocation`, maps coords to nearest city

